{"tid":1534231,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"進一步孤立黑警","createTime":"2019-09-03T02:50:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-03T05:48:56.000Z","uid":33939,"like":59,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"407b909aa33fc12abed04e2623fbb4278c1a4850","tid":1534231,"uid":33939,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T02:50:17.000Z","msg":"請大家晌social media，頭像/status等等，大量表明&quot;黑警不是我親友&quot;。要鋪天蓋地咁做。要成為社會嘅風向。要知道細路青年會容易受影響。跟住啲狗仔狗女就會同啲狗劃清界線。<br />\n<br />\n唔好睇少個成效，多人做，成本少，效果大！"},{"pid":"e73d71758425a62711b6e768cacfe21004d573bc","tid":1534231,"uid":69525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T02:50:31.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: small;\">我唔想知佢錄音內容<br />\n我推到同溫層既大家知道<br />\n你地負責幫手去fb啊等等宣傳得唔得<br />\n唔好再理膠post喇 關注返行動post<br />\n再好好運用6月至今每個核彈去twitter做文宣喇<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/twitter4HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Ftwitter4HK&d=xz9%2BKahtnlDLfwjNDOwuFBjXlokmAnOoGQHL1SEg040%3D&h=8ece844b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/twitter4HK</a><br />\n<br />\n[置頂] 建議9月8日百萬人大遊行/集會，<br />\n請求美國國會通過人權及民主法案<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1530650\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1530650</a><br />\n<br />\n901 機場測試係成功<br />\n辛苦曬行左20公里既手足 勿被帶風向<br />\n<br />\n908 我希望美國巴絲手足都有遊行<br />\n聲援香港同埋同要請求美國國會通過人權法!<br />\n<br />\n908 建議：<br />\n-大量英文文宣/紙牌<br />\n-高舉大量美國議員大頭相<br />\n-高舉大量國旗<br />\n-唔建議勇武，因為主題涉及美國<br />\n(另一原因係 廢時佢又區區有狗搜身兼 補充文具需時又珍貴)<br />\n-領事館門前唱國歌<br />\n<br />\n無人申請不反 都要照上街<br />\n需要文宣制圖 然後我幫你宣傳<br />\n由今日開始宣! 908照上街!<br />\n<br />\n建議內容copy某位巴打既<br />\n9月我要照上街<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"3e93bcce3cc36ce559351437928a2f9e24ae43dc","tid":1534231,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T02:50:59.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">9月8！到時見！</strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2GKH20p.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2GKH20p.png&h=6178433f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a5da11b0d8595ded8579915df91e91305d5fd0cf","tid":1534231,"uid":229436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T02:51:14.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"262cecd93edcf5ca9a42aba927782fa134696be7","tid":1534231,"uid":229436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T02:51:26.000Z","msg":"用埋同一張圖"},{"pid":"8fcd3a02ff1bbe7db0e12045db0b17e697aa969a","tid":1534231,"uid":209679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T02:52:01.000Z","msg":"整一張相出黎先得"},{"pid":"4601bd3812356c18b1b23ab76f54157985456603","tid":1534231,"uid":33939,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"262cecd93edcf5ca9a42aba927782fa134696be7","tid":1534231,"uid":229436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T02:51:26.000Z","msg":"用埋同一張圖"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T02:52:50.000Z","msg":"有冇人識設計，可以設計一張出嚟，做fb頭像。"},{"pid":"59a7a71bcae987768545f3674b7d700592156387","tid":1534231,"uid":46950,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T02:54:43.000Z","msg":"推呀"},{"pid":"233b89295f06eb433c3869ce58224cbf8f560c11","tid":1534231,"uid":33939,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T02:56:11.000Z","msg":"求設計宣傳圖片，頭像等。"},{"pid":"60177e39fd5a0c34b325922de0a6aeb393bf2d06","tid":1534231,"uid":33939,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"407b909aa33fc12abed04e2623fbb4278c1a4850","tid":1534231,"uid":33939,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T02:50:17.000Z","msg":"請大家晌social media，頭像/status等等，大量表明&quot;黑警不是我親友&quot;。要鋪天蓋地咁做。要成為社會嘅風向。要知道細路青年會容易受影響。跟住啲狗仔狗女就會同啲狗劃清界線。<br />\n<br />\n唔好睇少個成效，多人做，成本少，效果大！"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T02:59:08.000Z","msg":"仲有，當好多人做哩樣嘢嘅時候。狗或者狗仔女就會對全世界人都有戒心。變成自己獨立自己。<br />\n<br />\n而且，咁樣做係冇犯法。"},{"pid":"6e1b04f3a502f963f71bfdca2f9d53915dcfd685","tid":1534231,"uid":116486,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T0